[00:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'There are things we feel that no words can hold. Moments that stay quiet, alive only inside us. You see them when you close your eyes. You feel them when no one\'s looking. But how do you show them?'

[00:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'For a long time, only a few could. Artists, poets, dreamers. They found ways to turn feeling into form. The rest of us just kept it inside.'

[00:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'But now you can too. You can give shape to what you feel. Let your thoughts turn [music] into light, your emotions into movement, your imagination into something real'

[00:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'through AI that listens, that sees the spark behind your words and helps you bring it to life. So go ahead. Don\'t just say it, show it.'

[00:55] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Introducing Render Forest 1.0. What you feel made visible.'
